  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "07 people who tried to escape from the country are locked up",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "During a patrol carried out by the Sri Lanka Navy in the sea area off Thalaimannar yesterday (06th) night, 07 people suspected of illegally trying to migrate from Sri Lanka to a foreign country by sea were arrested along with 02 smugglers.",
        "A coastal patrol vessel belonging to the Sri Lanka Naval Vessels Tammanna of the North Central Naval Command inspected a suspicious dinghy sailing in the sea area off Thalaimannaram last night (06th). There, a man who was suspected of illegally trying to migrate to a foreign country by sea in the dinghy along with 07 people including 03 women and 03 small children and 02 smugglers involved in that smuggling were taken into the custody of the Navy along with the dinghy.",
        "The people taken into custody by the Navy were identified as residents of Kilinochchi and Pesale, aged between 09 and 43 months, and they were handed over to the Thalaimannar Police for further legal proceedings."
      ],
